	<div itemprop="text"><p>Well said &#8211; “You Can’t Stop Piracy, So Don’t Try.”</p>
<p>The only thing I want to add. Developers (of course, only a few) should also take a look on the pricing structure. If it is GPL licensed then don&#8217;t forget the morals of &#8220;Open source&#8221;. There are a lot of people want to spend money but some devs/designers have such pricing that they can&#8217;t even *afford* it.</p>
<p>On the other hand, there are a lot of developers who are just opposite in nature.</p>
