	<a class='comment-reply-link' href='/2011/why-you-should-use-gpl-for-commercial-themes/comment-page-1/?replytocom=7700#respond' onclick='return addComment.moveForm("div-comment-7700", "7700", "respond", "455")'>Reply to this comment</a>	</div>
